import { Route, Routes } from "react-router-dom"
import { ListGame } from "./listGame"

export const Routing=()=>{
    return <Routes>
        <Route path="liG" element={<ListGame></ListGame>}></Route>
        <Route path="liC" element={<ListGame></ListGame>}></Route>
        

    </Routes>
}
